rows.label: qst701706_msg0001
rows.name:
Bloody Lobsters? Of course I know
them, mo! The name of bad guys, mo!

rows.label: qst701706_msg0002
rows.name:
At Momimi's house, we were raised to
believe that bad kids get taken by the
Bloody Lobsters. It's incredibly scary, mo.

rows.label: qst701706_msg0003
rows.name:
Silent Specter? I've never heard
of that, mo. I'm sorry, mo.

rows.label: qst701706_msg0004
rows.name:
...Did you all perhaps
do something bad, mo?

rows.label: qst701706_msg0005
rows.name:
You should buy a blessed vase from
Momimi's place, mo. It will surely
bring you peace of mind, mo!!
